{"type":"message","id":"f283d8e5","parentId":"d554a442","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:12:02.372Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_94d0849dcb484627a1974035","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"WARN Discord slash commands have no allowlists\n    Discord slash commands are enabled, but neither an owner allowFrom list nor any per-guild/channel users allowlist is configured; /… commands will be rejected f…\n    Fix: Add your user id to channels.discord.allowFrom (or approve yourself via pairing), or configure channels.discord.guilds.<id>.users.\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n--\n│ Discord  │ ON      │ OK     │ token config (MTQ3…FRxM · len 72) · accounts 1/1                                      │\n└──────────┴─────────┴────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────┬──────────┬──────────────┬────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Key                                             │ Kind   │ Age      │ Model        │ Tokens                         │"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4906,"aggregated":"WARN Discord slash commands have no allowlists\n    Discord slash commands are enabled, but neither an owner allowFrom list nor any per-guild/channel users allowlist is configured; /… commands will be rejected f…\n    Fix: Add your user id to channels.discord.allowFrom (or approve yourself via pairing), or configure channels.discord.guilds.<id>.users.\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n--\n│ Discord  │ ON      │ OK     │ token config (MTQ3…FRxM · len 72) · accounts 1/1                                      │\n└──────────┴─────────┴────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────