{"type":"message","id":"716d85f7","parentId":"f283d8e5","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:12:12.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - Discord is configured and running. Let me check if the gateway is running properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Discord is configured and running** ✅\n\n```\nServer: 1475377083667583019\n├── requireMention: false ✓ (bot responds to all messages)\n├── groupPolicy: allowlist ✓ (restricted to your server)\n└── State: OK ✓\n```\n\n**One warning** about slash commands allowlist — you can fix this by adding your Discord user ID:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set channels.discord.allowFrom '[\"YOUR_DISCORD_USER_ID\"]'\n```\n\nOr just DM the bot once to pair, and it will auto-add you.\n\n**Ready to test!** Go to any channel in your server and send a message — no @mention needed."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":383,"output":173,"cacheRead":22336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772431922372}}
